<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4 font-semibold">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Le esclamazioni (o interiezioni) esprimono uno stato d'animo o una sensazione improvvisa (sorpresa, gioia, dolore, noia…). Sono seguite dal punto esclamativo o dai punti di sospensione.
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le <strong class="text-blue-600">esclamazioni proprie</strong> sono parole che si usano solo come esclamazioni: Ahi! Oh! Ohi! Ahia! Uffa! Boh! Suvvia! Ahimè!...</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le <strong class="text-green-600">esclamazioni improprie</strong> sono aggettivi, nomi, gruppi di parole usati come esclamazioni: Bene!, Aiuto!, Bravo!, Accipicchia!, Forza!, Meno male!, Mamma mia!...</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Collega ogni esclamazione all'emozione corrispondente.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Esclamazioni -->
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 mb-3">Esclamazioni</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Uffa!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Evviva!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Ahimè!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Ahi!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Boh!</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Emozioni -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4 border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 dark:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 mb-3">Emozioni</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>abbattimento</em> → Ahimè!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>noia</em> → Uffa!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>gioia</em> → Evviva!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>incertezza</em> → Boh!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>dolore</em> → Ahi!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      <span>Sottolinea esclamazioni proprie<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e esclamazioni improprie<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Ah</span>, non dire bugie!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Accipicchia</span>, che capitombolo!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Forza</span>! Ancora un po' e siamo arrivati.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Che bel lavoro: <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">brava</span>!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Mamma mia</span>, che spavento ho preso!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Ehi</span>, mi ascolti o parlo al vento?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Povero me</span>, sono proprio nei guai!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Uh</span>, come sei sfortunato!</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Scrivi una frase per ciascuna delle seguenti esclamazioni.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg mb-4">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        Bene!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        Zitto!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        Basta!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        Ohi ohi!
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-full md:w-4/5 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 focus:outline-none">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-full md:w-4/5 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 focus:outline-none">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-full md:w-4/5 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 focus:outline-none">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-full md:w-4/5 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 focus:outline-none">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
